      "text": "不在採買清單上\n的物品，忍耐3\n次才能購買",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "不在採買清單上\n的物品，忍耐3次才能購買",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "0El7c2-7D1w_XdFnWGG3d",
